{"tid":226331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 今日同女朋友係餐廳跳舞...","createTime":"2017-05-02T12:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T12:29:03.000Z","uid":87656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e99baf26a5d5d4491dae9796582e80a848129913","tid":226331,"uid":87656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"今日週年紀念日本來都book好間餐廳準備好哂<br />\n好衰唔衰訓撚過龍約左佢七點等點知七點先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間餐廳又話咩遲到十五分鐘就唔留位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有即刻打俾條女say sorry順便叫佢入去叫住野食等我<br />\n搞完一輪終於到餐廳我都預左條女西口西面架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我都有經驗扮哂冇事入去坐低攞張餐牌睇<br />\n一坐低我就問佢嗌左咩<br />\n點知佢冇西面佢伸手出黎話&quot;May I?&quot;<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖則間餐廳啲音樂都幾啱跳舞但大廳廣眾唔啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唯有笑笑口話&quot;咪玩啦食咩啫&quot;<br />\n點知佢又問多次May I?<br />\n唉屌難得佢冇西面咁我就死死地氣捉佢隻手出去跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知跳左幾步佢就話&quot;做乜撚野啫你?! 都話未嗌囉 俾個餐牌我啦仆街&quot; <br />\n到依刻先知自己柒左<br />\n最後成餐飯我都唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禮物都冇拎出黎"},{"pid":"2b021d30b26619d9ce706cf4a2e3c9763dc4e680","tid":226331,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fd55451a1974f6e759abdbc3c5b9bc6fddbbf8","tid":226331,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"呢個唔好笑"},{"pid":"309e8ff3d52c3ca1e9ac510e84b48a579c2feb85","tid":226331,"uid":37641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"f60ce8c6d67fb693655e56d032bdacc3b311cf35","tid":226331,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"無是咁的重作"},{"pid":"2ec6acfb598609a0d7d2530a782ebeab276a35c2","tid":226331,"uid":87656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個唔好笑</blockquote><br />\n點會好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家都唔敢面對條女"}]}